WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:01.239
A guy like you

2
00:00:01.240 --> 00:00:02.039
Came up with this plan

3
00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:04.239
Now Qín Shì has teamed up with Dōng Hǎi

4
00:00:04.240 --> 00:00:05.119
And other families

5
00:00:05.160 --> 00:00:06.679
To openly attack Fù Shì

6
00:00:07.120 --> 00:00:08.519
In just three days

7
00:00:08.640 --> 00:00:10.519
Its market value dropped by a hundred billion

8
00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:12.999
Now the shareholders

9
00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:14.239
Are rushing to sell their stocks

10
00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:15.519
Fù Shì

11
00:00:15.840 --> 00:00:17.159
Is about to collapse

12
00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:18.279
I don’t even know

13
00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:19.359
What kind of woman Qín Ruò Yǔ is

14
00:00:19.360 --> 00:00:20.199
What spell she cast

15
00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:21.039
To make Young Master Qín

16
00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:22.599
Unable to stay away from her

17
00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:23.759
Like he’s hypnotized all day

18
00:00:25.240 --> 00:00:25.999
Jiā Háo

19
00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:27.599
Look, I’ve done so much for you

20
00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:28.999
If not for merit, at least for effort

21
00:00:29.520 --> 00:00:31.319
Stop being mad, okay?

22
00:00:32.320 --> 00:00:33.399
Okay?

23
00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:33.999
Fine

24
00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:35.719
You cute little thing, stop acting all pitiful

25
00:00:36.120 --> 00:00:37.039
Let me tell you

26
00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:38.399
Since I met you

27
00:00:38.520 --> 00:00:40.479
I haven’t had a single good thing happen

28
00:00:40.560 --> 00:00:41.839
How was I so blind back then

29
00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:42.599
To ditch Qín Ruò Yǔ

30
00:00:42.600 --> 00:00:43.639
And choose you?

31
00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:44.799
Jiā Háo

32
00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:46.959
But I truly love you

33
00:00:47.040 --> 00:00:48.079
Stop pretending

34
00:00:48.720 --> 00:00:49.519
Let me tell you

35
00:00:49.760 --> 00:00:50.919
If Fù Shì doesn’t make it this time

36
00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:51.719
You can go sell

37
00:00:52.040 --> 00:00:52.999
Until Fù Shì is completely gone

38
00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:54.919
Then stop

39
00:00:54.920 --> 00:00:55.879
That’s it

40
00:01:04.600 --> 00:01:05.999
What a jerk

41
00:01:06.440 --> 00:01:08.119
If it weren’t for the boring Jiāng family

42
00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:09.239
Would I have followed you?

43
00:01:10.760 --> 00:01:11.599
Fù Jiā Háo

44
00:01:12.040 --> 00:01:13.759
You dare treat me like this

45
00:01:14.120 --> 00:01:15.719
I’ll make sure you face the consequences